{"tid":2494034,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得青沙公路(8號幹線)好浪費？","createTime":"2021-04-18T10:59:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T11:20:24.000Z","uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ae51b1fff350ea3aa8c89447ef1661214d2fd056","tid":2494034,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:59:21.000Z","msg":"以機場去沙田為例<br />\n行青馬+青衣北橋+城隧<br />\n里數又少啲 隧道費又平啲<br />\n<br />\n大西北去沙田就一定揀吐露港<br />\n<br />\n青衣上橋又淨係得貨櫃碼頭嗰邊一個入口<br />\n就算住青衣南都覺得遠....<br />\n<br />\n最ON9係昂船州大橋/南灣隧道一條大直路限80<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話限100都多啲車肯行吖 可以追返啲時間 又可以飛下車<br />\n<br />\n唯一嘅用處係咪俾啲人大西北來往西九<br />\n因為時間同里數都同3號幹線差唔多"},{"pid":"563bd8f5e215c1e131981a43722ada2983461024","tid":2494034,"uid":231179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:02:31.000Z","msg":"西九龍返沙田好快<br />\n<br />\n其實有條快路<br />\n對於我地小市民黎講一定係利多於弊"},{"pid":"8bf11d6074f082427e47c9dacbe785ee39c90e76","tid":2494034,"uid":372525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:03:56.000Z","msg":"好用wor 條路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb0b372200b7535c54aba3f68fda67bf6633696","tid":2494034,"uid":13914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:04:04.000Z","msg":"如果早40年就好有效益, 新界東去葵涌好快"},{"pid":"cd3c1676d14ece88af3c8cee38e1fe53e97c8e57","tid":2494034,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"563bd8f5e215c1e131981a43722ada2983461024","tid":2494034,"uid":231179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:02:31.000Z","msg":"西九龍返沙田好快<br />\n<br />\n其實有條快路<br />\n對於我地小市民黎講一定係利多於弊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:04:12.000Z","msg":"我知呀 呢個都好有用<br />\n<br />\n沙田＜&mdash;＞西隧/奧海城/西九係好快<br />\n但條昂船州大橋/南灣隧道好似浪費左"},{"pid":"df915148aa30653fedb827f6911c54f716d1b63b","tid":2494034,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:05:40.000Z","msg":"西隧行8幹返沙田大埔好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c744079cb02d1deb8ec894f2cbf098e4e195d1","tid":2494034,"uid":93600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:10:40.000Z","msg":"d出入口駁到錯晒 都唔知邊個設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5032783efdc608d9f0ae80fce110833a1e37817b","tid":2494034,"uid":301952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:12:36.000Z","msg":"真係for 九號碼頭啲貨櫃車岩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d246797822cc3e4ab95d153eefb108152ab620d","tid":2494034,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00c744079cb02d1deb8ec894f2cbf098e4e195d1","tid":2494034,"uid":93600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:10:40.000Z","msg":"d出入口駁到錯晒 都唔知邊個設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:13:01.000Z","msg":"地理限制"},{"pid":"aebdec3c602df6598c377a420ad5e8587f3e59ba","tid":2494034,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df915148aa30653fedb827f6911c54f716d1b63b","tid":2494034,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:05:40.000Z","msg":"西隧行8幹返沙田大埔好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:16:31.000Z","msg":"北大嶼都係八號幹線一部分...點會好浪費<br />\n但係中間昂船州大橋/南灣隧道又真係同三號幹線太近<br />\n而且南行落唔到大角咀果邊都做唔到分流的作用"},{"pid":"453eac3d83a5629d7dfac8324a354dd5f3471273","tid":2494034,"uid":44830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aebdec3c602df6598c377a420ad5e8587f3e59ba","tid":2494034,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df915148aa30653fedb827f6911c54f716d1b63b","tid":2494034,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:05:40.000Z","msg":"西隧行8幹返沙田大埔好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyT